{"tid":1778378,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟通過法案 擬制裁華官員","createTime":"2019-12-11T02:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T02:04:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"39b90c3beba2617914da08d8bad4050564a9b173","tid":1778378,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:01:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191211/DI6PYZAEX2VRQQCFLERU5TEVAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191211%2FDI6PYZAEX2VRQQCFLERU5TEVAM%2F&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwrO6ciNacqKxYXGqE8pVUEM%3D&h=6eb9a29e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191211%2FDI6PYZAEX2VRQQCFLERU5TEVAM%2F&h=9bbc696b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191211/DI6PYZAEX2VRQQCFLERU5TEVAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n歐盟通過法案 擬制裁華官員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191211/large/1575994971_ab21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191211%2Flarge%2F1575994971_ab21.jpg&h=e3c2b14b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n博雷利<br />\n<br />\n歐盟外長會議前日通過啟動制裁侵犯人權者法案的立法程序。這項歐盟版《馬格尼茨基法案》（Magnitsky Act）被視為歐洲發出維護人權的強烈訊號，未來將對侵犯人權的外國人，如中國官員等拒發簽證及凍結財產等。<br />\n<br />\n昨日是世界人權日，歐盟成員國外長前日齊集布魯塞爾召開會議，歐盟新任外交和安全政策高級代表博雷利（Josep Borrell）在會後記者會透露，在一些成員國要求下，會議同意啟動一項關於全球性制裁的籌備工作，以應對嚴重侵犯人權者的行為，相當於歐盟版本的《馬格尼茨基法案》。預料立法程序需時數月。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭人權法明年初實施<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：上訴存變數 遮面須承擔風險<br />\n<br />\n美國2015年通過簡稱《馬格尼茨基法案》的《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，該法案的最初版本2012年通過，僅針對罰導致俄羅斯稅務顧問馬格尼茨基（Sergei Magnitsky）等死於莫斯科獄中的普京政權官員，措施包括禁止入境，並將他們的美國資產交給聯邦政府。「全球版」用於制裁全球侵犯人權者。<br />\n<br />\n近年來中國因迫害新疆維吾爾族人及侵犯香港自由人權，國際上制裁聲浪漸高，除美國外，荷蘭國會近期率歐盟之先，通過要求荷蘭政府必須2020年1月31日前實施其荷蘭版本的《馬格尼茨基法案》。被制裁者未來將被禁止入境荷蘭，並且凍結他們的資產。<br />\n<br />\n自由歐洲電台／中央社"},{"pid":"4c55ec078a9ce8f7c1e1ed04d4b264967868ea0d","tid":1778378,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:03:06.000Z","msg":"華=有香港身份證人士？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f43b6c0fd9b32f822edfa5740f65ecba0a48347","tid":1778378,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:03:12.000Z","msg":"通過<span style=\"color: red;\">啟動</span>制裁侵犯人權者法案的<span style=\"color: red;\">立法程序</span><br />\n<br />\n唔好做標題黨"},{"pid":"b29ab2d5149b75d7a18dedad992711d5f4bbc1c6","tid":1778378,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T02:04:15.000Z","msg":"通過= through<br />\n唔係pass"}]}